<!DOCTYPE html> 
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="https://dcassetcdn.com/design_img/10150/25224/25224_294121_10150_image.jpg" type="image/x-icon">
    <title>Recipe List</title>
    <style>
       /* General body styling */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            background: white;
        }

        /* Header styling */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(223,17,17,1) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,1) 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        /* Recipe list container */
        .recipe-list {
            margin: 20px;
        }

        /* Set up the grid for the recipe list */
        .recipe-list ul {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* Recipe list items */
        .recipe-list li {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .recipe-list li:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        /* Recipe list images */
        .recipe-list img {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Recipe list links */
        .recipe-list a {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #ff6347;
        }

        /* Recipe list descriptions */
        .recipe-list p {
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Add Recipe button styling */
        #addbtn {
            display: block;
            margin: 20px auto;
            width: 200px;
            padding: 15px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
            text-align: center;
        }

        #addbtn:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* Footer styling */
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }

        /* Responsive Styles */
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            header {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                padding: 15px;
            }

            .recipe-list {
                margin: 10px;
            }

            .recipe-list li {
                padding: 10px;
            }

            .recipe-list a {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

            .recipe-list p {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            header {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                padding: 10px;
            }

            .recipe-list {
                margin: 5px;
            }

            .recipe-list li {
                padding: 8px;
            }

            .recipe-list a {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .recipe-list p {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }

            footer {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Non Veg Recipes List</h1>
    </header>
    
    <section class="recipe-list">
        <ul>
            <li>
                <img src="https://feastwithsafiya.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/easy-chicken-biryani.jpg" alt="Non Veg Recipe">
                <a class="page-title" data-title="Chicken Biryani"href="/recipes">Chicken Biryani</a>
                <p> I show you how to make an aromatic, delicious and the best Chicken Biryani.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <img src="https://www.wellplated.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Authentic-Indian-Butter-Chicken-recipe.jpg" alt="Chicken Curry">
                <a class="page-title" data-title="Butter Chicken"href="/recipes">Butter Chicken</a>
                <p>Lip-smacking and delicious dish.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <img src="https://sodelicious.recipes/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/fried-fish-tips-e1530181241241.jpg" alt="Vegetable Stir-fry">
                <a class="page-title" data-title="Fish Fry"href="recipes">Fish Fry</a>
                <p>Crispy, delicious and flavorful fish fry.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <img src="http://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2313/8987/articles/Rogan_Josh_01_copy_1200x1200.jpg?v=1625548245" alt="Tacos">
                <a class="page-title" data-title="Mutton Rogan Josh"href="/recipes">Mutton Rogan Josh</a>
                <p>Kashmiri-style mutton curry.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <img src="https://www.whiskaffair.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Punjabi-Egg-Curry-2-1.jpg" alt="Margherita Pizza">
                <a class="page-title" data-title="Egg Curry"href="/recipes">Egg Curry</a>
                <p> Learn how to make delicious and protein-rich curry.</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <button id="addbtn" onclick="location.href='/addrecipes'">Add Recipes</button>
    <script>
        // Step 2: JavaScript to handle clicks
    document.querySelectorAll('.page-title').forEach(function(anchor) {
        anchor.addEventListener('click', function(event) {
            event.preventDefault(); // Prevent default anchor click behavior
            const title = this.getAttribute('data-title'); // Fetch the title
            const targetUrl = '/recipes?title=' + encodeURIComponent(title); // Construct the target URL
            window.location.href = targetUrl; // Redirect to the new page
        });
    });
    </script>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Delicious Recipes. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
